{subhead}Payback To Be Ported To Intent, AmigaDE and Apple Mac{def}
{left}
{pp}
According to  Virtual Programming, Payback is currently being ported to
several new platforms. Apex Designs are coding the Intent/AmigaDE version in-house
and the Mac conversion is being developed by an expert coder working for VP.
{pp}
Payback is a port of the classic Grand Theft Auto game.
{pp}